lead_paragraph: FC Midtjylland's joy at beating Fremad Amager in a cup tie on Thursday was short-lived as the players returned to their dressing room to discover it had been broken into.

headline.print_headline: Midtjylland Suffer Dressing Room in Break-In During Cup Win
headline.main: Midtjylland Suffer Dressing Room in Break-In During Cup Win
